partnerDetails.about: ZAK Solutions is an industry-recognized market leader in the region for secure and business-aligned IT services. With this unique understanding, ZAK Solutions goes beyond simply selling approach to effective solutions design. ZAK has taken significant strides towards enhancing its reputation as aggressive, "Sure-footed", innovative, and "leading edge". We are specialized in delivering high-quality solutions and services ranging from project management, consultancy, implementation and after sales support. ZAK Solutions serves a diverse variety of industry sectors, providing a wide range of corporate solutions and managed IT services that enable companies to focus more on their core businesses.
